SUMMARY:In My Dreams
DESCRIPTION:Vibrant love\, just out of reach. \nLUDMI on vocals\, Aman Mahajan on piano\, and Rohit PS on drums move between original music and reimagined jazz standards\, drawing on flavours from across the world. Inspired by LUDMI’s debut single In My Dreams\, this is an evening of longing. Voice\, piano\, and drums respond to each other in real time: a concert in conversation.  \nComposition and improvisation. Structure and spontaneity. Intimate and expansive.  \nSupported by: \n \n
URL:https://bangaloreinternationalcentre.org/event/in-my-dreams/
LOCATION:Bangalore International Centre\, 7\, 4th Main Road\, Domlur II Stage\, Bangalore\, Karnataka\, 560071\, India
CATEGORIES:Music,Performing Arts
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://bangaloreinternationalcentre.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Thumbnail_IMD.jpg
END:VEVENT
